title: WP.Residence.Wordpress.Theme.V1.0.4-XTHEMEWP.COM
description:
Name: WP Residence - Real Estate WordPress Theme
Type: Wordpress Theme
Release Date: 6 August 14
Version: 1.0.4
Columns: 4+
Compatible Browsers: IE9, IE10, IE11, Firefox, Safari, Opera, Chrome
Software Version: WordPress 4.0, 3.9
Compatible With: Facebook, WPML, Bootstrap 3.x
Layout: Responsive
Files Included: PHP Files, HTML Files, CSS Files, JS Files
Widget Ready: Yes
Released By: XthemeWP.com

WP Residence is designed for Real Estate independent agents and agencies, but you can also allow other people to submit their properties for free, for a fee or based on a monthly subscription.

In WP Residence you can create your own custom property fields, and you can add custom Advanced Search spots with your own fields. You can add up to 8 spots Search includes AJAX SEARCH in map, with results opening in the same page or in a new page.

If you like it, please support the creators and buy it! This theme seriously Kick Ass!
